data.title: Wikipedia:WikiProject Ukraine/Cleanup listing
data.text:
This is an automatically generated cleanup listing.

NOTE: WolterBot has not been run since 2010. Live cleanup listings are at: https://bambots.brucemyers.com/cwb/index.html

The listing is based on a database snapshot of 12 March 2010. It contains all articles flagged for cleanup which are tagged with {{WikiProject Ukraine}} on their talk page.

Based on that data, 2866 articles are assigned to this project, of which 1156, or 40.3%, are flagged for cleanup.
